":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9E5","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":37547,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/16\/abandons-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37081,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Whoever abandons the prayer commits unbelief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe covenant between us and them is the prayer, so whoever abandons it has committed unbelief.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2621 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0628\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0647\u0652\u062f\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37417,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/23\/taqseer-salah-journey\/","url_meta":{"origin":37081,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Sunnah to shorten prayer during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Muwarriq al-\u2018Ijli reported: He asked Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, about prayer during travel. Ibn Umar said, \u201cTwo cycles, two cycles. Whoever opposes the Sunnah has disbelieved.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf 'Abd al-Razza\u0304q 4281 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0648\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0651\u0642\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u062c\u0652\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u0636\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37577,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/umar-tarak-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37081,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Salat: No share of Islam for one who leaves prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miswar ibn Makhramah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThere is no share of Islam for one who abandons the prayer.\u201d Source: al-Muwat\u0323t\u0323a' 117 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0631 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0645\u064e\u062e\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0638\u0651\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37579,"url":"h